                <td bgcolor="#ECECEC" valign="top"><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;08/07/2003&nbsp;: 6:01:41 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> <br />OK, well, this item is better for any necro at low levels since mana regen spells don't take much hp from you ... It really loses value imo as you gain levels unless you are an iksar ... Since it will stack with your natural regen ... A 51 Iksar with Zlandi heart, +3innate regen will heal 1 point per tick using Lich (49 mana regen) ... (I think sitting only, not standing) I would never use this item except for twinking an Iksar Necromancer ... I am 65 and I would sell it in a heartbeat because it would be useless to me ... I would rather use my dagger with 100+ HP, nicer stats ect ... Solo, you want to damage the MoB of course, so forget about regen and just use dmg over time life taps to get your health back or regular life taps ... Regen at 65 isn't even an issue imo, at least it isn't to me ... So bottom line I think this is a twink only item ... <br /><br />Also to any necros that don't instant invis Circlet of "Shadow" GET IT! ... It is probably the best necro item you could ever get ... I don't care if some greedy bastard wants 30k for it, if I didn't have it, I would pay ... It is worth every penny ... <br /><br />Also, don't worry about epic, it is worthless unless you just want to do it for a status symbol ... But, it is easy for me to say it is worthless when I have better, so maybe it would be good for some people, but the darkness cast takes so long, I only used it for farming and on MoBs that didnt run away just for a mana free extra Dot ... I also heard Epic might be upgraded eventually ... So who knows ... <br /><br />Also, make sure you get any of the quest robes (or PoG) robe that has infinite cast of conjure corpse ... If you ever get in a raiding guild it is a must ... <br /><br />Also if you have the means, get a second account on a second computer and get any character up to level 45+ so you can sacrifice him for free essence emeralds ... If not they are pretty expensive on a lot of servers ... 400pp each on Stormhammer usually ... Free is always better ... <br /><br />Also, get a mount asap ... on a lot of raids, sitting is bad ... It could ruin the entire raid if MT loses agro because of someome sitting .... Happened to us earlier .... Raid wasnt ruined, but MT did lose agro and it did cause more havok then it usually would have ... Also you might just die from sitting if you get agro from anything ... I know spectre regen cant use mounts (which is why it sucks) But when you get SoS you go back to a skeleton and it is all good from there :) I recommend a lizard instead of a horse ... I hate that damn horse head getting in the way of my view ... <br /><br />Anyway, just a few of my opinions .... Good luck on your necros :) <br /><br /><br /><br /></span></font></td>
